<item>
            <title>[LU-831] struct bit field type should be unsigned type</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-831</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;struct bit field type should be unsigned type, or else when they are read out through proc interface, they are showed as a big number equivalent to -1. &lt;br/&gt;
e.g.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;cat /proc/fs/lustre/obdfilter/lustre-OST0000/read_cache_enable&lt;br/&gt;
4294967295&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</description>
